  {
    "name": "Web.presets",
    "options": [],
    "default": "[New Preset]",
    "text": "",
    "tooltip": "Select a setting preset to apply. You can also save your own presets to use at a later date.<br />Available Presets:<br />Season 6:<br />The competitive settings for MMR Standard Season 6.<br /><br />Blitz:<br />Blitz Settings - meant for highly competitive play and short seeds.<br /><br />Allsanity (in 3 different variants):<br />The hardest settings you can imagine. Everything is enabled, and different requirements make the difference. Use this if you want to test your limits and how deep your MM knowledge reaches.<br /><br />Advanced:<br />A challenge for those who want to prove their knowhow of glitches and strats. These settings expect you to get your items in unorthodox ways more often than not, and hints and mechanics might be more complex than you are used to.<br /><br />Classic:<br />Classic MMR Racing settings improved with modern conveniences. Relive season 1/2 settings with a twist.<br /><br />Modern:<br />The competitive settings for the previous MMR Standard season, but without a random starting mask.<br /><br />SG Live 2025:<br />The competitive settings for the SG Live 2025 tournament.",
    "type": "Presetinput",
    "shared": false
  },
